name: Busted! #7
description:
The seventh edition of Busted! is a special Leo birthday edition. It was created over the week of my birthday, 8/18/21. Dedicated to all the Leos out there.
This is the first timed edition of the series. Available for 72 hours when first released.
5400x7200px 300dpi jpeg
8/26/21

Busted! is a weekly series of psychedelic explorations of the sculptural ephemera of our collective past.  (All images used are either my own artwork or sourced from the public domain collections of various libraries and museums.  No copyrighted or stock images used.)
